videos.description: Off a Syracuse miss, Louisville's Quentin Snider  sprints past a Syracuse defender and lays it in.
videos.headline: Snider scores past  a couple Syracuse defenders

videos.description: Off a missed 3-pointer, Syracuse's Tyler Lydon skies in for a putback dunk.
videos.headline: Lydon flies in for the putback slam

videos.description: Louisville head coach Rick Pitino on his team heading into the locker room with the lead
videos.headline: Louisville head coach Rick Pitino on his team heading into the locker room with the lead

videos.description: Syracuse's John Gillon sends a great pass inside to a cutting Andrew White III who lays it in.
videos.headline: Gillon's pass sets up a White III score

videos.description: Louisville's Quentin Snider tosses a long alley-oop to Donavan Mitchell who catches and dunks with one hand.
videos.headline: Mitchell catches and slams vicious alley-oop

videos.description: Frank Howard attacks the lane, goes to the glass to score and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Howard goes to the glass to score and draw the foul

videos.description: After Syracuse nearly turns it over, Andrew White III flips the ball to John Gillon who knocks down a 3.
videos.headline: Wild sequence ends in a Syracuse 3-pointer

videos.description: Louisville's Jaylen Johnson slams in a putback dunk, then Syracuse responds with a 3-pointer from John Gillon.
videos.headline: After huge dunk, Syracuse answers to head to overtime

videos.description: Syracuse's Tyler Robinson misses 2 shots at the line, Louisville rebounds and holds on to win.
videos.headline: Missed free throws cost Syracuse the game late in overtime

videos.description: Louisville's Ryan McMahon on his overtime performance
videos.headline: Louisville's Ryan McMahon on his overtime performance

videos.description: No. 8 Louisville gets 16 points from Donovan Mitchell and survives a road conference test by defeating Syracuse 76-72 in overtime.
videos.headline: Louisville edges Syracuse in overtime
